..
.. This file is included in the rst_prolog to set up substitutions.
..

.. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

.. appname: Replaced with the application name in appropriate style.

.. |appname0| raw:: html

    <span class="appname">

.. |appname1| raw:: html

    </span>

.. |appname| replace:: |appname0|\ |project|\ |appname1|

.. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

.. block-image: Makes sure the next text does not overlap the previous floating
   image.

.. |block-image| raw:: html

   <p class="after-image">&nbsp;</p>

.. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

.. nbsp: Inserts a non-blocking space character.

.. |nbsp| raw:: html

   &nbsp;

.. ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

